Introduction

Yong Junhyung is a South Korean singer-songwriter, rapper, and producer under his own independent label Black Made. He is a former member of the boy groups Highlight (formerly BEAST) and XING under the name Poppin Dragon.

He made his solo debut on December 13, 2013, with his first mini-album Flower.
